{"tid":1623407,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［推上國際］Mask Challenge For Hong Kong Campaign","createTime":"2019-10-04T21:03:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T14:21:30.000Z","uid":270504,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a7adcb04fa16aab52045473ae02185c9ff139076","tid":1623407,"uid":270504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T21:03:31.000Z","msg":"禁蒙面法已經立法。香港人退無可退，要運用群眾和網絡力量向極權的香港政府反抗。<br />\n<br />\n今次蒙面法只係個幌子，為引用緊急法試水溫；緊急法繞過所有立法程序，毫無法理上嘅制衡，以「行政」完全凌駕「立法」，係「三權分立」遭破壞嘅鐵證，全力反對蒙面法、反對引用緊急法破壞法治！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地要將呢單野推上國際</span></span><br />\n<br />\n而家誠邀大家參加<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Mask Challenge for Hong Kong</span></span><br />\n<br />\n只要係各大社交平台 e.g. Facebook、Instagram、Twitter、Reddit 等<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">1. 上載一張戴口罩/面罩/豬咀嘅相</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yh6TczK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyh6TczK.jpg&h=5daee42f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">2. 加以下Hashtag</span><br />\n#maskchallenge<br />\n#maskchallengeforhongkong<br />\n#saynotoantimasklaw<br />\n#freehongkong<br />\n#4october<br />\n#hongkong<br />\n#香港人加油 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">3. tag朋友</span><br />\n至少3個香港朋友及2個海外朋友，再Retweet，如此類推<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">推出國際 坐言起行<br />\n推畀更多人知 更多人做！</span></span> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外提醒大家 <br />\nPost相上社交平台有一定風險<br />\n建議將風險減到最低：<br />\n<br />\n1）Set privacy 唔好public<br />\n2）搵乾淨背景<br />\n3）遮耳遮眼<br />\n4）手足以自己曝光率/行幾前/有冇點過相<br />\n<br />\n自行判斷風險<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jkk8LTP.com\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJkk8LTP.com&h=b07f2b7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KfUtMaD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKfUtMaD.jpg&h=9281a4ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iw3ioXj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fiw3ioXj.jpg&h=50d1f2c4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"95b49f862b1a509b1db4e3a6958ea0759f5817bd","tid":1623407,"uid":230942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T21:09:27.000Z","msg":"蒙佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78ab62f78ab21c81293d802e03d6a095389467f0","tid":1623407,"uid":229517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T21:42:26.000Z","msg":"一定要Tag外國朋友"},{"pid":"004699b7a5c35521a2aa2174c69a1614f5e2054c","tid":1623407,"uid":149021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T14:14:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"80b2a8939258fb9313306b932080e291ffa3053b","tid":1623407,"uid":49359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T14:21:30.000Z","msg":"尋晚我訓唔著都諗要整過challenge<br />\n要名人留言支持一d支共唔認同價值<br />\n但佢唔留言支持就會俾西方批評<br />\n迫佢係兩邊選一個"}]}